# packages/vscode (@prism-ai/vscode)

VS Code extension. Currently a stub; Phase 5 adds Activity Bar panel, WebviewPanel (D3 graph), TreeDataProvider, MCP host on localhost:7474.

## Layout

- **src/extension.ts** — activate/deactivate. Will register commands (prism.vizOverview, prism.traceSymbol, prism.buildFromSelection), panels, and MCP server.

## Rules

- Use @prism-ai/core and @prism-ai/mcp. Extension hosts or connects to MCP; no duplicate GTR logic.
- Dependencies: @types/vscode, no LLM SDKs. Follow VS Code extension API and activation events for performance.
